Class TextDataConvertor

    • net.librec.job.progress.ProgressReporter

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, DataConvertor, Progressable

    public class TextDataConvertor
extends AbstractDataConvertor
    A TextDataConvertor is a class to convert a data file from CSV format to a target format.

        itemIds - itemId to itemIndex map
